<br />
<p>Ed Yong is an <a href="http://blogs.discovermagazine.com/notrocketscience/2010/10/14/i%E2%80%99d-like-to-thank-the-academies/">award-winning</a> British science writer. His work has appeared in New Scientist, the Times, WIRED, the Guardian, Nature and more. Not Exactly Rocket Science is his attempt to talk about the awe-inspiring, beautiful and quirky world of science to as many people as possible.
