		</li><li id="text-10" class="widget widget_text"><h2 class="widgettitle">Do you want to be a science writer?</h2>			<div class="textwidget">Read <a href="http://blogs.discovermagazine.com/notrocketscience/2010/07/29/on-the-origin-of-science-writers/">origin stories and advice</a> from over 130 science writers from around the world. </div>
